powerBank.name: KC certified mobile charger 10000 mAh
powerBank.desc1: Fashionable and elegant, multiple colors shipped randomly
powerBank.desc2: Compatible with most mobile phone fast charging protocols on the market
powerBank.functionValue: Multiple U port outputs, multiple voltages, and built-in screen display
powerBank.commentText1: COD 2S$, it's real, I got it.
powerBank.commentText2: Real event, real prize, the price is only S$2.
powerBank.commentText3: The customer service is gentle and beautiful, helping me to get the prize, thank the customer service!
powerBank.commentText4: Won it in the lottery, only 2S$, good charging effect, large battery capacity, give 2 stars.
powerBank.commentText5: 10000 mAh also supports three different charging interfaces, so affordable!
powerBank.commentText6: COD only 2S$ received this power bank in a week!
powerBank.commentText7: The customer service is very beautiful, the voice is very nice, my prize was shipped very quickly, received it in 5 days.
powerBank.commentText8: Only 2S$, if this power bank is not in my hand, I will not believe it!
powerBank.commentText9: I won this power bank, only 2S$, so lucky!
powerBank.commentText10: My friend and I both won this power bank, haha!
powerBank.commentText11: It is about the same size as a mobile phone, 2S$ COD is too cost-effective
powerBank.commentText12: The customer service responded quickly. This is what I am most satisfied with. Of course, the price is only 2S$, which is also super affordable
powerBank.commentText13: I can't believe that I bought this power bank for 2S$
powerBank.commentText14: A very good event to win a power bank. I hope there will be more such lottery activities in the future!

oneZhe.name: 【PANDA】Apple 15 brand new and unopened
oneZhe.desc1: 6.7-inch Super Retina XDR display, ProMotion adaptive refresh rate technology
oneZhe.desc2: New ways to interact with the Ludo Island feature and iPhone
oneZhe.desc3: Water-resistant, can stay underwater for up to 30 minutes at a depth of 6 meters
oneZhe.desc4: 48MP main camera, 12MP ultra-wide-angle camera and 12MP telephoto camera, 4K video shooting
oneZhe.desc5: 12-megapixel front-facing camera with TrueDepth, supporting portrait mode and smart HDR
oneZhe.desc6: A17 Pro chip, 6-core CPU, 6-core GPU, 16-core network engine
oneZhe.desc7: Face ID, SOS emergency contact car accident detection, USB-C interface
oneZhe.commentText1: The one I drew was S$420, but I didn’t win the S$180 one, but it was still very cheap.
oneZhe.commentText2: Cash on delivery has free shipping and you can check your phone before paying, which is great
oneZhe.commentText3: It is confirmed that it is indeed a lucky draw jointly organized by bites and panli. I really want to have more chances to win more lucky draws and win more mobile phones!
oneZhe.commentText4: I won the lottery for S$180 and sold it to my friend for S$600, hahaha
oneZhe.commentText5: When I first received the power bank, I thought it was a scam, but I didn’t expect that the phone also arrived the next day.
oneZhe.commentText6: I thought it was a lie to me, but I didn’t expect that I actually received it. I like it very much. I will help you promote it.
oneZhe.commentText7: Buying a brand new iPhone15 for S$180 is the luckiest thing in my life!
oneZhe.commentText8: A joint event between bites and panli, I was lucky enough to win the iPhone15 haha
oneZhe.commentText9: The customer service responded quickly and the iPhone15 I received is very easy to use.
